x4freetext: After irradiation in Gammasphere the samples
were measured for radioactivities using a
well-calibrated HPGe detector in the Center for
Accelerator Target Science Counting Laboratory.
It was assumed that the charge distributions of
neighboring isobaric chains are similar and
radionuclide yields from a limited mass region can be
used to determine a single charge distribution curve
for that mass region
